<p>
  <span class="nym">Absalom</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Hebrew</span> <i>אַבְשָלוֹם</i> 'father of peace'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a Biblical son of King David. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Absalon</i>. Geneva Bible (1560): <i>Abshalóm</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>For more information see <span class="bibl"><span class="key">Withycombe</span>, <span class="loc">s.n. Absalom</span></span>.</p>
  
  


